replies.body:
I want Garen to win, but based on how they fare in game as well as their comparable roles in the lore, I'd say slight edge to Darius in a straight up fight. If Garen were able to play a bit more like a guerrilla fighter and move in and out of combat, use his bush ambushes, use his  (recently buffed) healing, then I think Garen could win in a longer duel where he doesn't allow himself to fall to execute range for darius. Very close and kind of situational in my opinion. Edge goes to Darius but I'm rooting for Garen.

